ement between these results and\nour sub-Alfv\\'enic simulations when viewed with the magnetic field in the\nplane-of-the-sky (especially when sensitivity limitations are considered),\nthough the observations are also consistent with an intermediately inclined\nmagnetic field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Mar 2023 18:45:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
